channel.title: RuneScape's Loader Files [to make rs' webclient?]
channel.description:
Hello. I have been messing around with the Java Cache Viewer and i have found some of RuneScape's Loader files. I am not sure if this is the right section, please move to appropriate section if needed.
So.. Loaders: So far I have the world130 loader.jar file. I will be updating as I find more. **NOTE** TO DOWNLOAD ANY LOADER FOR YOURSELF, SIMPLY TAKE THE URL: http://world#.runescape.com/loader1764106967.jar AND CHANGE THE WORLD# TO THE WORLD YOU WISH TO DOWNLOAD THE LOADER FROM. **NOTE**
I'm not sure whether the loader is the same for every single world, but I hope this is useful to anyone.
World1 Loader.jar Original Website: http://world1.runescape.com/loader1764106967.jar Mirrored [if needed]: RapidShare: http://rapidshare.com/files/287133337/loader1764106967_2_.jar.html Uppit: http://uppit.com/v/W10DBFWG
World130 Loader.jar Original Website: http://world130.runescape.com/loader1764106967.jar Mirrored [if needed]: MediaFire: http://www.mediafire.com/?w4mtmnjztwd RapidShare: http://rapidshare.com/files/287132066/loader1764106967.jar.html Uppit: http://uppit.com/v/XEAQO7CM [if you need more mirrors, please just say and I will add.
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------- DECOMPILED LOADER.RAR I have Decompiled the jagexloader, from world130. There aren't many classes, and the total file size is pretty small, but I know that the c.class[c.java] contain the main_file_cache.dat# and the game_unpacker. It also contain the 3d library codes, and the game code loader. I'm pretty sure this should help people replicate the rs webclient, or help in the hacking of it. I hope this help!!
Links: RapidShare: http://rapidshare.com/files/287136564/loader1764106967.rar.html MediaFire: http://www.mediafire.com/?j2in2hywmzt Uppit: http://uppit.com/v/qbvjuy4s
kthxbai. Grim.
